      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "STARLIGHT JEWEL (4) ran a decent 23.15 when winning over 400m at this track last start. Has the ability and looks a key chance again. BALI UNLEASHED (8) flew the lids from out wide with a slick early split but ran over at the finish when a narrow fourth (23.37) over 400m at this track. Safe beginner but wide box to overcome and will need some luck. In the mix. CLOSE SHAVE (2) turned in a better run last time to find a minor placing (23.31) at this track behind STARLIGHT JEWEL in a Other. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Safe beginner who has drawn to advantage. Expected to feature again. MAGIC NANCY (6) can fill a top-three spot.",
